   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Aurelius Philippos and his associates, overseers of the chaff, to Palemon, greeting. Has brought Pemen, . . ., your own man, for the villagers(?) . . ., 100 litrai on account, (and) for the villagers(?) . . . 50 litrai on account. [Year 18] and 17 and 10, [- - -] 25.</ab>
